title: Reptile-ownership : household penetration rates 2007 to 2013
summary: Overall Penetration rates has decreased over the Year.
Penetration rates is roughly constant from 2007 to 2008, gradually decreasing from 2008 to 2009, slightly increasing from 2009 to 2010, and lastly roughly constant from 2010 to 2012.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2008 and 2009.
Maximum Penetration rates, about 2.1 was reported at Year 2008
Minimum Penetration rates about 1.5 was reached at Year 2009
